page.content:
ALL OF THE PUPILS IN THE 2nd YEAR IN ROMAN HILL MIDDLE SCHOOL IN SUMMER '85 CONTRIBUTED TO THE DOMESDAY SURVEY. HERE ARE JUST A FEW : AMANDA PEEK: SARAH CROWE: JOANNE HOWES: JAYNE DUNNELL: CATHERINE ROWSE: DARREN SOUTHGATE: LINDA HOOK: ALICE SPARKSMAN: MARK JACOBS: IAN JOHNSON: SHELLEY PEARSON: JONATHAN ROLL: TARA STANLEY: SHERRYL HARVEY: DANIEL CLARKE: SHAUN FLAXMAN: MATTHEW PANTER: LOUISA CREEDON: HEIDI LUCAS: ANTHONY NORMAN: CRAIG GROOM AND MATTHEW ALLISON.
TEACHER IN CHARGE: MRS. S. WOODARD.
